        </item>
        <item>
            <title>内置 AI 晶片提升声画质素   LG 发表全新 OLED 电视支援 144Hz 更新率</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/04/lg-reveals-new-oled-tvs-with-high-144hz-refresh-rates-ahead-of-ces-2024/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lg-reveals-new-oled-tvs-with-high-144hz-refresh-rates-ahead-of-ces-2024</link>
