        </item>
        <item>
            <title>黑客新招式盗用 Google 帐户，官方一键解决问题教学</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/malware-abuses-google-oauth-endpoint-to-revive-cookies-hijack-accounts/tech-secure/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=malware-abuses-google-oauth-endpoint-to-revive-cookies-hijack-accounts</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/malware-abuses-google-oauth-endpoint-to-revive-cookies-hijack-accounts/tech-secure/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 13:30:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[资讯保安]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[chrome]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Cookie]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[google]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1212904</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>据外媒报道，有多个黑客团体正在使用浏览器内置 Cookie 的漏洞，用恢复 Cookie 的方式入侵受害者的 Google、 Facebook 等帐户，入侵后即使原用家登出或更改密码亦没有用，黑客仍然可继续登入受害人的帐户。Google 早前回复 9to5Google 指已经有解决方式。</p><p>据外媒 BleepingComputer 报道，部分黑客最近使用浏览器里面的 Cookie 验证漏洞，以代替受害人验证帐户，达致入侵其帐户的目标。具体操作手法是黑客会先诱导用户安装钓鱼程式，然后该些程式会拦截用户经 Google Chrome 储存的登入认证 Cookie ，并尝试利用这些 Cookie 入侵受害人的帐户。</p><p>这个漏洞最麻烦之处是用户不能够利用登出或更改善密码这类别方式去解决被入侵问题，因为黑客可以长期透过 Cookie 继续攻击受害者，入侵其帐户。</p><p>幸而 Google 回复 9to5Google，表示已升级 Google Chrome，现时用户可以在设定里选择「你与 Google」，看见你的头像后就可以点击旁边「关闭」按钮，就可以彻底登出并取消被黑客攻击的装置。要留意的是，此举会在这部电脑登出你的 Google 帐户。</p><h2>Step 1 开启 Chrome，点击右上角的三点</h2><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212915" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/1-694x251.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="251" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/1-694x251.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/1-768x278.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/1.jpg 1277w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲开启 Chrome 后，点击右上角的三点（绿色框示）</p><h2>Step 2 选择设定</h2><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212917" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2-327x580.jpg" alt="" width="327" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2-327x580.jpg 327w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2.jpg 475w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 327px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择设定（绿色框示）</p><h2>Step 3 选择「你与 Google」，再选择「关闭」</h2><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212916" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/3-694x496.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="496" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/3-694x496.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/3-1259x900.jpg 1259w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/3-768x549.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/3.jpg 1273w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲先点击左上角的「你与 Google」，再点击右边的「关闭」</p><h2>Step 4 点击关闭</h2><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1212924" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/萤幕撷取画面-2024-01-03-185612.jpg" alt="" width="637" height="259" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「关闭」</p><h2>Step 5 重新登入你的 Google 帐户</h2><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212927" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/5-522x580.jpg" alt="" width="522" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/5-522x580.jpg 522w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/5.jpg 562w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 522px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲此时重新登入便可</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/malware-abuses-google-oauth-endpoint-to-revive-cookies-hijack-accounts/">Bleeping Computer</a>、<a href="https://9to5google.com/2024/01/02/google-account-cookies/">9to5Google</a>、<a href="https://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/56484">自由时报</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/malware-abuses-google-oauth-endpoint-to-revive-cookies-hijack-accounts/tech-secure/">黑客新招式盗用 Google 帐户，官方一键解决问题教学</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/malware-abuses-google-oauth-endpoint-to-revive-cookies-hijack-accounts/tech-secure/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【教学】游日本旅客必装 Safety Tips App    海啸、地震、紧急事故即时有通知</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/japan-safety-tips-app/software/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=japan-safety-tips-app</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/japan-safety-tips-app/software/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 13:00:39 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Android App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[应用软件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅游]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Safety tips App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[地震预警]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[日本]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[海啸预报]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1212929</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今年元旦日本石川县发生黎克特制 7.6 级强烈地震，其后伴随著数十次余震，摧毁大量房屋及公路，能登半岛地区与外界交通一度中断。专家指未来一周仍然有机会发生大规模地震，因此建议游客可下载日本官方推出的「Safety Tips」灾害情报 App。</p><p>Safety Tips 是个免费应用程式，由日本政府官方推出，支援 iOS 及 Android 平台。当用家身处日本时，可以立即收到地震、海啸等警告资讯，支援繁体中文、英文及多国语言。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212941" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/萤幕撷取画面-2024-01-03-193238-327x580.jpg" alt="" width="327" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/萤幕撷取画面-2024-01-03-193238-327x580.jpg 327w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/萤幕撷取画面-2024-01-03-193238-507x900.jpg 507w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/萤幕撷取画面-2024-01-03-193238.jpg 692w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 327px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Android 版本下的地震通知，图片来源：<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.rcsc.safetyTips.android">Google Play</a></p><p>用户最多可预先设定 5 个关注地点，针对性接收当地各种灾害讯息。这款式应用程式会提供气象、地震、火山爆发等通知，同时亦会提供接收外国人的医疗机构、紧急联络处等资讯。除此之外，这款应用程式亦会提供避难讯息、疏散建议等。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212977" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-01-03-192902-1280x655-1-694x355.jpg" alt="Japan 救急 app" width="694" height="355" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-01-03-192902-1280x655-1-694x355.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-01-03-192902-1280x655-1-768x393.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-01-03-192902-1280x655-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/safety-tips/id858357174">Apple App Store</a></p><h2>下载连结：</h2><p><a href="https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/safety-tips/id858357174">iOS</a><br /><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.rcsc.safetyTips.android">Android</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/japan-safety-tips-app/software/">【教学】游日本旅客必装 Safety Tips App    海啸、地震、紧急事故即时有通知</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
