            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div class="x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a"><div dir="auto">Disney 旗下著名动画角色米奇（Mickey Mouse）于《Steamboat Willie》亮相的版本根据美国版权法规定，在今年元旦正式进入公有领域，来自美国的导演 Jamie Bailey 随即与其团队在 YouTube 上传了第一条以 Mickey Mouse 为主角的恐怖电影《Mickey&#8217;s Mouse Trap》的预告片。</div><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212974" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-01-03-72426-513x580.jpg" alt="" width="513" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-01-03-72426-513x580.jpg 513w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-01-03-72426-796x900.jpg 796w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-01-03-72426-768x868.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-01-03-72426.jpg 1338w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 513px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><p>《Mickey&#8217;s Mouse Trap》故事背景设定于女主角 21 岁生日当日，由于她要在游乐场上班，因此无法与朋友庆祝生辰。女主角的朋友决定给她一个惊喜，在游乐场为女主角庆祝生日，可是一个头戴 Mickey Mouse 面具的杀手混入了乐园，因此主角需要用尽一切方法，逃离杀手的追捕。</p></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212934" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/412840269_737827935071907_5231297061018041740_n-1-694x448.png" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/412840269_737827935071907_5231297061018041740_n-1-694x448.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/412840269_737827935071907_5231297061018041740_n-1-1280x826.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/412840269_737827935071907_5231297061018041740_n-1-768x495.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/412840269_737827935071907_5231297061018041740_n-1-1536x991.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/412840269_737827935071907_5231297061018041740_n-1-2048x1321.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/412840269_737827935071907_5231297061018041740_n-1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto">电影中除了杀手头戴 Mickey Mouse 面具外，预告片中亦有不少《Steamboat Willie》的元素，配合预告片上传的时间，可见拍摄影团队早就对 Mickey Mosue 版权进入公共领域一事做好准备。</div><div dir="auto"></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212884" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-0-31-screenshot-694x295.png" alt="" width="694" height="295" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-0-31-screenshot-694x295.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-0-31-screenshot-1280x545.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-0-31-screenshot-768x327.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-0-31-screenshot-1536x654.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-0-31-screenshot-2048x871.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-0-31-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲预告片中可见《Steamboat Willie》的海报，图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kAg7laUDXX4">YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212885" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-1-0-screenshot-694x295.png" alt="" width="694" height="295" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-1-0-screenshot-694x295.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-1-0-screenshot-1280x545.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-1-0-screenshot-768x327.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-1-0-screenshot-1536x654.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-1-0-screenshot-2048x871.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-1-0-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kAg7laUDXX4">YouTube</a></p><p>《Mickey&#8217;s Mouse Trap》编剧兼制片 Simon Philips 接受 BBC 采访时表示，他们仅是想制作一部有趣的电影，同时又称，如果继续将 Mickey Mouse 放在阖家欢电影里面，那么永远不会有突破，因此他们想做一些与 Mickey Mouse 以往形象有很大反差的事。现阶段 Simon Philips 尚未透露电影何时上映，但消息指预计将于今年 3 月上映。</p><p>Mickey Mosue 并非第一个被套进恐怖电影的 Disney 角色，2022 年 Disney 旗下角色 Winnie the Pooh 就抢先步进入公共财产领域，其后英国导演 Rhys Frake-Waterfield 自编自导《Winnie-the-Pooh: Blood and Honey》电影。剧情讲述 Christopher Robin 上大学后就抛弃了小熊维尼与小猪，于是他们就大开杀戒。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212891" src="https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MV5BNGMwNjBlM2MtYzFlNi00ZDgwLTkwN2QtMjgzOWVjMWQ4NzAzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDA1NDA2NTk@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_-454x580.jpg" alt="" width="454" height="580" srcset="https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MV5BNGMwNjBlM2MtYzFlNi00ZDgwLTkwN2QtMjgzOWVjMWQ4NzAzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDA1NDA2NTk@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_-454x580.jpg 454w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MV5BNGMwNjBlM2MtYzFlNi00ZDgwLTkwN2QtMjgzOWVjMWQ4NzAzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDA1NDA2NTk@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_-704x900.jpg 704w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MV5BNGMwNjBlM2MtYzFlNi00ZDgwLTkwN2QtMjgzOWVjMWQ4NzAzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDA1NDA2NTk@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_-768x982.jpg 768w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MV5BNGMwNjBlM2MtYzFlNi00ZDgwLTkwN2QtMjgzOWVjMWQ4NzAzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDA1NDA2NTk@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 454px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt19623240/">IMDb</a></p><p>初代 Mickey Mouse 于 1928 年，在黑白动画短片《Steamboat Willie》中首次登场，至今已历经 95 个寒暑，其与初代 Minnie Mouse 版权亦正式在今年元旦日到期，意味着创作者不需再经由 Disney 许可或付费就能够使用这个版本的 Mickey Mouse。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_96091"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kAg7laUDXX4?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-67861538">BBC</a>、<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" dir="auto" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kAg7laUDXX4&amp;ab_channel=SimonPhillipsActor">Simon Phillips Actor@ YouTube</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/mickey-mouse-horror/movie-2/">Mickey Mouse 版权元旦到期，美国导演即上传 Mickey 恐怖片预告</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
